{"tid":900744,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"藍塘傲12伙減價最多15%平過去年3月 個別劈價250萬","createTime":"2018-11-13T13:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T02:42:28.000Z","uid":216432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f9b7b91ff6a4bd1a1ff006be044d025dfac3e4","tid":900744,"uid":216432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"19:17 2018/11/13<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帝國集團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麗新繼旺角逸新、筲箕灣逸瑆後，再將為旗下新盤劈價推售。<br />\n與帝國集團合作的將軍澳現樓盤藍塘傲剛修改價單，12伙單位定價調低，減價幅度由5%至14%，有10伙單位平過去年最初定價，例如8座16樓G室，實用面積634平方呎，最新定價1,530.6萬，較2017年7月最初定價1,779.7萬減價249.1萬，減幅達14%；7座16樓F室，最新定價1,317.5萬元，較去年3月定價1,532萬，減價214.5萬，減幅亦達14%，意味單位最少重返去年初價。<br />\n付款方法方面，今次未有如之前逸瑆般增加大量優惠，只有新增年底前入市的10萬元定價折扣作為「尊尚傢俬」優惠。另引入1080日長成交期付款，另有提前付清樓價現金回贈。<br />\n以180天即供連同新增10萬優惠計，較去年最初折實價實際平5.3%至14.7%不等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2207456/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2207456%2F&d=YuHE%2FmQVi5mMJQIqXTrZGp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cc551885\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2207456/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2207456/cvvn20181029001_09_1024x1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2207456%2Fcvvn20181029001_09_1024x1024_1024.jpg&h=aa543cf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83db454bab850a4b253f0ef96027b226f3010c5f","tid":900744,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"第一槍"},{"pid":"998afd9eb830ddcce09e93bc885f6100dd58ca66","tid":900744,"uid":216432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"邊個減價邊個係鬼"},{"pid":"2157b23b99414e1389580d1ea76d5ee290890947","tid":900744,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"麗新可以正名叫業主擊狙手"},{"pid":"2bbab8cd9b957c35780df90c40a88127850c14f3","tid":900744,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"樹倒猢猻散？<br />\n<br />\n郭生一去即減價"}]}